# --------------------------------------------------------------------------
# CONFIGURACION RUTAS PROGRAMA  (Relative to DOCUMENT_ROOT)

	RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d
	RewriteRule ^(.*)$ index.prg/$1 [L]
</IfModule>
